flowPara.flowSpan: : (a) ERPs on scalp averaged over subjects. Divergences in activity arise at occipital area when comparing target vs. non-target trials. (b) Average over subjects of brain activity (top), signed point-biserial correlation coefficient (r2) along time (bottom) and scalp plot of these quantities (middle) averaged over significative time intervals (different gray shades in top and bottom plots). These intervals were obtained based on r2 values.
